  "detailed_description": "Luminoso is a puzzle game with laser beams. The goal of each puzzle is to make all laser beams hit the receiver pieces of their respective color.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many unique piece types, each with different effects.<br></li><li> Lasers may have different beam colors. Colors can be mixed to produce new colors, or split into their component colors.<br></li><li> 60 hand-crafted levels with varying difficulty.<br></li><li> A level editor to create your own levels.<br></li><li> Chilling music that doesn't get on your nerves.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Luminoso is a puzzle game with laser beams. The goal of each puzzle is to make all laser beams hit the receiver pieces of their respective color.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many unique piece types, each with different effects.<br></li><li> Lasers may have different beam colors. Colors can be mixed to produce new colors, or split into their component colors.<br></li><li> 60 hand-crafted levels with varying difficulty.<br></li><li> A level editor to create your own levels.<br></li><li> Chilling music that doesn't get on your nerves.</li></ul>",
